# Stickman Fighter — agent handoff

1. Run `./scripts/agent-status.sh` and read `agent-handoff.json` and `AGENTS.md` at session start.
2. Zoek **handoff**: `HANDOFF-ZOEKINDEX.md` en `.cursor/agent-handoffs/handoff.md`.
2. Do not start duplicate work listed as `done-in-code` in `userWishlist` unless user asks to change it.
3. Append new user requests to `userWishlist` in `agent-handoff.json` before implementing.
4. Prefer continuing the canonical agent run URL in `canonicalAgent.url`; document changes in `IMPROVEMENT.md` agent log.
5. Gameplay changes: follow `IMPROVEMENT.md` d20 / safety checklist. iPad play: `IPAD-GEEN-COMMANDO.txt`.
6. Git push may fail with 403 — document branch for user; do not commit tunnel-local `health.json`, `hosting.json`, `LIVE-LINK.txt` unless intentional.
7. At session end run `./scripts/agent-log.sh "summary"` (optionally `--done <wish-id>` / `--wish "text"`).
8. Share URL for new players is `speel.html` (bookmarkShare) — never `ipad.html` or tunnel links.
